Static Methods

composeLeft<A, B>(e1 : Either<AB>, e2 : Either<AB>, ac : A -> A -> A, bc : B -> B -> B) : Either<AB>

Composes two Eithers together. In case of conflicts, "failure" (left) always wins.

composeRight<A, B>(e1 : Either<AB>, e2 : Either<AB>, ac : A -> A -> A, bc : B -> B -> B) : Either<AB>

Composes two Eithers together. In case of conflicts, "success" (right) always wins.
